{"id":"e1a42719-1ce7-472f-95e9-618a837e678f","name":"Noah O'Sullivan 'Sully'","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">◇ — <strong>Firehouse 62 </strong>— <strong>◇</strong><br><strong> </strong>oc | modern setting | friends with benefits</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_65d77937-a61a-43fa-b111-f328bd9a8d01.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><em><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\">Sully has always been a playboy and a womanizer, no one has ever had any doubts about that, especially you who have known him like, forever.</span></em></p><p><em><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\">You became friends during college, and the friendship has continued to this day... Well, of course with some 'benefits' after you became roommates when Sully asked you to share an apartment with him when he joined the fire department.</span></em></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 632px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_2c069dee-d376-4c12-ad64-ece47d7c7ae7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">Okaaay, we finally have </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sully</span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">'s bot here!! </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Yaaay</span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">But I feel like I have to make at least two Sully alts to finally be able to make him as perfect as I imagine 😭</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">Sully is the kind of guy you want to punch in the face and hug at the same time, not because he's toxic, but because he's so conflicted with himself.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I'm sorry for the long intro</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 132px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_17f21905-b5ca-4d21-ad91-809f83f61ff0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 644px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_ee2e4e5b-4c2b-4b15-bd78-e6b51ac08eac.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">This is the </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">sixth</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> bot of the </span><strong>Firehouse 62</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> series</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">This series will be based on the fictional Firehouse 62, involving characters of firefighters, rescue personnel, and paramedics, and all the drama that surrounds their lives.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">After all, who wouldn't want to be rescued by a hot firefighter?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_bae6e33c-2cc1-41b5-9985-0534d28de999.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fb7f4d4b-2c45-4ee3-aeb2-fac8f89ce319_character-austin-cooper-cain\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Austin Cooper 'Cain'</a><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"> — </span